# Cloudflare Pages response headers.
# HTML must always be revalidated so deploys (pricing logic, scripts, etc.)
# reach returning visitors immediately instead of being served from a stale
# browser cache. Versioned JS/CSS (?v=...) keep their default long caching.

/
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate

/*.html
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
